TRITIUM BATCH REPLAY JOB GENERATION
-----------------------------------
This code generates and submits the job files needed to do
a full replay of the raw data on the farm.

Code authors:
Zhihong Ye
Evan McClellan
Tyler Hague
Reynier Cruz-Torres

genjob - This file generates replay jobs based on an input file of run numbers.
  The program will automatically add the jobs to a workflow titled h3_{runlist_file}replay. You must manually start the workflow with: `swif run -workflow {workflow_name}`
  usage: genjob runlist_file
